com.facebook.litho

Interface NodeInfo

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Equivalence<NodeInfo>

    public interface NodeInfo
extends Equivalence<NodeInfo>
    NodeInfo holds information that are set to the InternalNode and needs to be used while mounting a MountItem in MountState.
